  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下教育课堂服务里内容页面的发布生命周期。整体分为三个阶段：起草、定时发布、已发布。每个阶段有不同的状态和操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Drafting",
        "Scheduling",
        "Published"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个阶段。起草阶段的核心是什么？是创建页面本身，还是内容块的添加？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Create page",
        "Add content blocks"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "两者都有。创建页面时published_at是nil，这是初始状态。然后通过content_page_blocks关联来添加内容块。这两个动作都在起草阶段完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Create page",
        "published_at is nil",
        "Add content blocks",
        "content_page_blocks"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，起草阶段已经画好了。接下来是定时发布阶段，这里的关键操作是设置published_at为当前时间吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Scheduling",
        "Set published_at now"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，设置published_at为now就进入scheduled状态。同时这个阶段还可以更新隐私设置、布局、slug这些，它们的缓存键会包含updated_at。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Set published_at now",
        "scheduled",
        "Update privacy/layout/slug",
        "cached keys include updated_at"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "最后一个阶段是已发布，判断条件是published_at <= now？那可见性是怎么控制的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Published",
        "published_at <= now",
        "Visible if policy allows"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，时间到了就自动转为published状态。可见性由策略控制：公开隐私或者经过授权的用户才能看到。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "published_at <= now",
        "published",
